  "page": "Vaes Graddakh",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"thumb tright\">\n<div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\">\n<div style=\"position: relative; border: 1px solid lightgray\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Essos.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Vaes Graddakh is located in Essos\"><img alt=\"Vaes Graddakh is located in Essos\" src=\"/images/thumb/2/28/Essos.png/300px-Essos.png\" width=\"300\" height=\"284\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/2/28/Essos.png/450px-Essos.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/2/28/Essos.png/600px-Essos.png 2x\" /></a><div style=\"position: absolute; z-index: 2; top: 28.3%; left: 52.5%; height: 0; width: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"><div style=\"position: relative; text-align: center; left: -4px; top: -4px; width: 8px; font-size: 8px; z-index:100;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/8px-Red_pog.png\" title=\"Vaes Graddakh\" width=\"8\" height=\"8\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/12px-Red_pog.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/16px-Red_pog.png 2x\" /></div><div style=\"font-size:&#160;%; line-height: 110%; z-index:90; position: relative; top: -1.5em; width: 6em; left: 0.5em; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"padding: 1px;\">Vaes Graddakh</span></div></div></div>\n<div class=\"thumbcaption\">Essos and the location of Vaes Graddakh\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<p><b>Vaes Graddakh</b> is a ruined city in northern <a href=\"/index.php/Essos\" title=\"Essos\">Essos</a> along the shore of the <a href=\"/index.php/Shivering_Sea\" title=\"Shivering Sea\">Shivering Sea</a>. It is situated at the eastern end of the <a href=\"/index.php/Sarne\" title=\"Sarne\">Sarne</a> delta, southeast of <a href=\"/index.php/Morosh\" title=\"Morosh\">Morosh</a> and east of <a href=\"/index.php/Saath\" title=\"Saath\">Saath</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtloiafcentral_essos.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtloiafcentral_essos.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> It was originally called <b>Sarys</b>, but it is now known by its <a href=\"/index.php/Dothraki_language\" title=\"Dothraki language\">Dothraki language</a> name, Vaes Graddakh, meaning \"City of Filth\".<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rawoiafvaes_graddakh_.28sarys.29.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rawoiafvaes_graddakh_.28sarys.29.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Vaes_Graddakh&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Sarys and its sister city, <a href=\"/index.php/Saath\" title=\"Saath\">Saath</a>, fought the <a href=\"/index.php/Ibbenese\" title=\"Ibbenese\">Ibbenese</a> for control over the mouth of the <a href=\"/index.php/Sarne\" title=\"Sarne\">Sarne</a> on several occasions.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafbeyond_the_free_cities:_ib.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafbeyond_the_free_cities:_ib.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Sarys was the last city of the <a href=\"/index.php/Kingdom_of_Sarnor\" title=\"Kingdom of Sarnor\">Kingdom of Sarnor</a> to be conquered by the <a href=\"/index.php/Dothraki\" title=\"Dothraki\">Dothraki</a> during the <a href=\"/index.php/Century_of_Blood\" title=\"Century of Blood\">Century of Blood</a>. It had already been largely abandoned by the <a href=\"/index.php/Sarnori\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Sarnori\">Sarnori</a>, however, before Khal <a href=\"/index.php/Zeggo\" title=\"Zeggo\">Zeggo</a> sacked it and put it to the torch.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rawoiafvaes_graddakh_.28sarys.29.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rawoiafvaes_graddakh_.28sarys.29.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafbeyond_the_free_cities:_the_grasslands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafbeyond_the_free_cities:_the_grasslands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Vaes_Graddakh&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtloiafcentral_essos.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtloiafcentral_essos.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Lands_of_Ice_and_Fire\" title=\"The Lands of Ice and Fire\">The Lands of Ice and Fire</a></i>, Central Essos.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rawoiafvaes_graddakh_.28sarys.29.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rawoiafvaes_graddakh_.28sarys.29.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">2.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rawoiafvaes_graddakh_.28sarys.29.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\">2.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_World_of_Ice_and_Fire\" title=\"A World of Ice and Fire\">George R. R. Martin's A World of Ice and Fire</a></i>, Vaes Graddakh (Sarys).</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiafbeyond_the_free_cities:_ib.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafbeyond_the_free_cities:_ib.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, Beyond the Free Cities: Ib.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiafbeyond_the_free_cities:_the_grasslands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafbeyond_the_free_cities:_the_grasslands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, Beyond the Free Cities: The Grasslands.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403095441\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.053 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.105 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 913/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 12406/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 4484/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 1871/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 13/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 2649/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   86.097      1 -total\n 38.83%   33.433      1 Template:Location_map\n 34.81%   29.974      1 Template:Location_map+\n 33.50%   28.845      5 Template:Ref\n 26.89%   23.148      1 Template:References\n 25.23%   21.721      1 Template:Location_map~\n 16.37%   14.097      5 Template:Ref/core\n  8.33%    7.175     22 Template:Location_map_Essos\n  4.80%    4.130      3 Template:Location_map/decdeg\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:14273-0!canonical and timestamp 20260403095441 and revision id 282541\n -->\n",
